FirstBank Nigeria said it has launched a designed website that has been upgraded with features streamlined to reinforce its role in delivering seamless banking and technology solutions to its customers. In a statement, the bank said the website is configured with modern design and improved functionality that eases customer experience whilst carrying out various activities on the site, including electronic banking. Non-customers are also able to open an account, putting them at an edge in the industry as they establish a relationship with the Bank that puts YOU, its customers, First. The new website adopts a fresh, magazine-style look and feel for easy navigation in order to promote the access to essential information for its customers, FirstMonie agents, prospective agents and the public. Commenting, Dr Adesola Adeduntan, CEO of FirstBank Group, said: “As one of the key contact points to existing and potential customers, the Bank’s website remains a gateway to our business, supporting our unique value propositions and financial services solutions.